  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 orphan claim)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. A credibility claim is asserted regarding mesh-independence and turbulence model adequacy; supporting evidence reports are referenced in the narrative but no structured provenance link is established from the claim node to any evidence artifact.",
