    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors. Seven factors were assessed and all achieved levels fall below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing epistemic gaps. A credibility claim regarding mesh-independence and turbulence model adequacy has been asserted based on the grid convergence study and turbulence sensitivity analysis described in the evidence reports; the claim is considered credible by the team and the package is accepted for regulatory submission pending gap closure.",
